A tree stump is a type of scenery left on the ground when a weathered dead tree has been chopped down. A stump will respawn into a dead tree after a short amount of time. The tree stump has no interaction options.

Strangely, the weathered dead tree stump variant is used when cutting down a maple tree in Miscellania. When a maple tree is cut down anywhere else, a maple tree stump is used instead.

A '''tree stump''' is a type of scenery left on the ground when a weathered [[Dead tree (weathered)|dead tree]] has been chopped down. A stump will respawn into a dead tree after a short amount of time. The tree stump has no interaction options.

Strangely, the weathered dead tree stump variant is used when cutting down a [[maple tree]] in [[Miscellania]]. When a maple tree is cut down anywhere else, a [[Tree stump (maple)|maple tree stump]] is used instead.
